          - rid: 1516066228257685510
          statUsed: 0
          output: 'To erect an idol of our sect upon the most sacred ground in the
            Empire? Such a decision truly demanded immense courage. Naturally, all
            other cults forged a brittle alliance to ensure the monument was removed,
            and after a bitter struggle, they emerged victorious. We lost many of
            our people, yet our bravery shall be remembered, and along with it, our
            statue!

            [Gained 20 Flock & 60 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685511
          - rid: 1516066228257685512
          statUsed: 2
          output: 'To erect an idol of our sect upon the most sacred ground in the
            Empire? Such a decision truly demanded immense courage. Naturally, all
            other cults forged a brittle alliance to ensure the monument was removed.
            However, our sect is not like the rest. Each of our brothers fought with
            the ferocity of ten men, and in the end, our casualties were light. The
            remaining fragments of the statue shall be exhibited in our temple as
            proof of our glory!

            [Gained 40 Flock & 100 Zeal]

'
